Generic single-database configuration with async SQLAlchemy support for SQLite.

## Usage

### Create a new migration
```bash
cd services/data-api
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of changes"
```

### Apply migrations
```bash
cd services/data-api
alembic upgrade head
```

### Rollback migrations
```bash
cd services/data-api
alembic downgrade -1
```

### View migration history
```bash
cd services/data-api
alembic history
alembic current
```

